item.title: Welcoming the Future
item.description: Hi there! My name is Angel. Join me as I embark on this blogging journey, where I’ll share my experiences, insights, and enthusiasm for data engineering, analytics, and artificial intelligence. Who Am I? I am a Data and Analytics Engineer by trade, who has also architected data solutions at an enterprise scale. My journey began at GameFly as a Business Analyst Intern, where I was later hired full-time after completing my Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science from CSU Fullerton.
